QuestData.Title: Well, Tell the Lady
QuestData.Description: <Thorodir breathes a deep sigh of relief.>$b$bThat's that, I'd say. The Banks are largely safe now, thanks to you. We can handle the rest of the cleanup on our own now.$b$bThe Lady of the Falls will want to hear of your success here. Why not go tell her the good news?
QuestData.LogDescription: Report to the Lady of the Falls in Glitterfall Basin.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Report to the Lady of the Falls in Glitterfall Basin.
QuestData.RewardText: Ah, that is wonderful news. Thank you for your assistance.
